\F[10]\AA[F]That being said, we have to find the last
\c[14]cipher\c[0]!
That being said...\c[14]it might be better to give up.

The fact that they're not even giving us a hint means they never
intended to give us the answer in the first place.

Or another thing... \c[14]We don't know if that cipher can really
be used for escape\c[0].

We must not forget that this is a battle against the main force
of the \c[14]Demon King's army\c[0]....

\F[15]\AA[F]........... (I, I've been honestly collecting them,
but....)

\F[10]\AA[F](There's no proof that these numbers... can really be
used, right?)
Wh, what!? Directly into my brain....
Finally, my voice has reached you♡
addLog ハヤト「敵じゃない...の？」
addLog セリア「精霊の友達！」
\F[3]\AA[F]Um... Didn't you return to the spirit world?

I intended to, but... It seems like some sort of mechanism is
preventing me from leaving this place.

\F[37]\AA[F]What did you say... So even if we hypothetically
gathered the four-digit code.........

Hayato: So you're saying we can't escape unless Sadi undoes the
spell. The issue wasn't even about the code after all....

You're probably right. That's why Anthurium... \c[14]was
searching for the weapons storage room\c[0].

The \c[14]storage room\c[0], which is Anthurium's old haunt, is not
affected by this spell.... That's why there should be a clue to
escape there.

\F\c[14]\AA[F]Hey, Hayato! You can handle that \c[14]weapon\c[0],
can't you? After all, you're the \c[14]hero's younger brother\c[0]!

Hayato: ............I'm sorry, Seria. What do you mean by
'weapon'\c[0]?

\F[10]\AA[F]Ah, yes. There were powerful weapons in the church
basement from the beginning, right? You, who have been living in
Variente, would know... right?
Hayato: {...Are you talking about the \c[14]Holy Sword\c[0]?

\F[10]\AA[F]\c[14]Holy Sword\c[0]... It's definitely strong, isn't
it!! So, Anthurium! Have you found that room?
Please come near me, Seria. I will use [Teleport]....
....Isn't that terrible, Anthurium♡ After I was so kind to you...♡
Lady Sadi.......? This is bad! His interference...!!
